    <briefdescription>
<para>DAC (Digital-to-Analog Converter) driver. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Thin wrapper over <ref refid="syn__port__dac_8h" kindref="compound">syn_port_dac.h</ref>, mirroring the pattern of <ref refid="syn__adc_8h" kindref="compound">syn_adc.h</ref>. Provides raw-count, millivolt, and percent write helpers.</para>
<para>Usage: <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="structSYN__DAC" kindref="compound">SYN_DAC</ref><sp/>dac;</highlight></codeline>
